    "start_animations": "{\n  \"orderedKeys\": [\n    \"4cac595c-21ff-44b3-99e3-ae5581dce64d\",\n    \"d08a764b-39d4-4404-82ff-27a92ca5683a\",\n    \"6f3b17d3-5f95-4148-a03e-8445ec6441fd\",\n    \"98625045-58ca-4dc4-ab1f-b98ad738549e\",\n    \"666ce23f-8833-4ea0-be68-debc739e9fab\",\n    \"f36627f2-07e3-4953-bb78-53672ef46128\"\n  ],\n  \"propsByKey\": {\n    \"4cac595c-21ff-44b3-99e3-ae5581dce64d\": {\n      \"name\": \"apple\",\n      \"sourceUrl\": \"/api/v1/animation-library/level_animations/4E1cFRl9ojrmIuPaSxS0.Rj25geUJMFX/lb-apple.png\",\n      \"frameSize\": {\n        \"x\": 68,\n        \"y\": 74\n      },\n      \"frameCount\": 1,\n      \"looping\": true,\n      \"frameDelay\": 12,\n      \"version\": \"GNSjtpec1oN8hVb1Q4e9ozDF639mKO7h\"\n    },\n    \"d08a764b-39d4-4404-82ff-27a92ca5683a\": {\n      \"name\": \"carrot\",\n      \"sourceUrl\": \"/api/v1/animation-library/fCiFCbsTDOoiLsbStivUZ249XH0TOxIY/category_food/carrot.png\",\n      \"frameSize\": {\n        \"x\": 78,\n        \"y\": 70\n      },\n      \"frameCount\": 1,\n      \"looping\": true,\n      \"frameDelay\": 2,\n      \"version\": \"fCiFCbsTDOoiLsbStivUZ249XH0TOxIY\"\n    },\n    \"6f3b17d3-5f95-4148-a03e-8445ec6441fd\": {\n      \"name\": \"strawberry\",\n      \"sourceUrl\": \"/api/v1/animation-library/level_animations/xsHnSJ0f2KxpiefM3vxEwAJJZJuatHbC/lb-strawberry.png\",\n      \"frameSize\": {\n        \"x\": 75,\n        \"y\": 89\n      },\n      \"frameCount\": 1,\n      \"looping\": true,\n      \"frameDelay\": 12,\n      \"version\": \"kGKIzqW15wGxQ5tAvC5NacACGz9Ppk0n\",\n      \"categories\": [\n        \"food\"\n      ]\n    },\n    \"98625045-58ca-4dc4-ab1f-b98ad738549e\": {\n      \"name\": \"orange\",\n      \"sourceUrl\": \"/api/v1/animation-library/level_animations/7pqH0HXQlqxv4FSDOnRuXzqDnJpzTaOj/lb-orange.png\",\n      \"frameSize\": {\n        \"x\": 75,\n        \"y\": 75\n      },\n      \"frameCount\": 1,\n      \"looping\": true,\n      \"frameDelay\": 12,\n      \"version\": \"9LzXo243pPLbuutYxgGyDlwArI5PRKgJ\",\n      \"categories\": [\n        \"food\"\n      ]\n    },\n    \"666ce23f-8833-4ea0-be68-debc739e9fab\": {\n      \"name\": \"broccoli\",\n      \"sourceUrl\": \"/api/v1/animation-library/level_animations/JnhnsjZCJfi60nzOFaf_nTwzGmU_lKZY/lb-broccoli.png\",\n      \"frameSize\": {\n        \"x\": 75,\n        \"y\": 76\n      },\n      \"frameCount\": 1,\n      \"looping\": true,\n      \"frameDelay\": 12,\n      \"version\": \"ZynOgauk.nclVOYzsf3GHdc_2mlRMIVD\",\n      \"categories\": [\n        \"food\"\n      ]\n    },\n    \"f36627f2-07e3-4953-bb78-53672ef46128\": {\n      \"name\": \"corn\",\n      \"sourceUrl\": \"/api/v1/animation-library/level_animations/ToKIQX2KuRC0HdNrkLb2TdJUpUrg2WTh/lb-corn.png\",\n      \"frameSize\": {\n        \"x\": 75,\n        \"y\": 73\n      },\n      \"frameCount\": 1,\n      \"looping\": true,\n      \"frameDelay\": 12,\n      \"version\": \"qNTUt1EzkF4S5UiuuyZ06veXRcFpnKyC\",\n      \"categories\": [\n        \"food\"\n      ]\n    }\n  }\n}",
    "start_blocks": "//Left Eye Variables\r\nvar leftEyeX = randomNumber(155, 165);\r\nvar leftEyeY = randomNumber(165, 175);\r\nvar leftEyeWidth = randomNumber(10, 50);\r\nvar leftEyeHeight = randomNumber(10, 50);\r\n\r\n//Right Eye Variables\r\nvar rightEyeX = randomNumber(235, 245);\r\nvar rightEyeY = randomNumber(165, 175);\r\nvar rightEyeWidth = randomNumber(10, 50);\r\nvar rightEyeHeight = randomNumber(10, 50);\r\n\r\n//Mouth Variables\r\nvar mouthX = randomNumber(150, 170);\r\nvar mouthY = randomNumber(230, 250);\r\nvar mouthWidth = randomNumber(65, 95);\r\nvar mouthHeight = randomNumber(15, 45);\r\n\r\n//Draw the background\r\nnoStroke();\r\nbackground(\"green\");\r\n\r\n//Draw the Face\r\nfill(\"yellow\");\r\nellipse(200,200,200,200);\r\n\r\n//Draw the Eyes\r\nfill(\"black\");\r\nellipse(leftEyeX,leftEyeY,leftEyeWidth,leftEyeHeight);\r\nellipse(rightEyeX,rightEyeY,rightEyeWidth,rightEyeHeight);\r\n\r\n//Draw the Mouth\r\nfill(\"white\");\r\nrect(mouthX,mouthY,mouthWidth,mouthHeight);\r\n",
    "libraries_enabled": "false",
    "contained_level_names": [
      "CSD U3L7 - Predictv2Embed_2023"
    ],
    "teacher_markdown": "**This can be overwhelming!** There are so many variables being used just to represent three different parts of the face. This is intentional, and students should rightly comment on how complicated this is. This discussion helps motivate the video in the next level, which introduces the concept of a Sprite that can help simplify our code when creating complex animations.",
